      <title>朝鲜废除与韩国经济合作的法律</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-08/north-korea-strikes-down-laws-on-economic-cooperation-with-south</link>
      <description><![CDATA[朝鲜议会废除了与韩国经济合作的法律，在领导人金正恩新年伊始表示不可能寻求和平统一后，邻国之间的矛盾进一步加深。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-08/north-korea-strikes-down-laws-on-economic-cooperation-with-south</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 08 Feb 2024 03:47:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国前国防部长魏凤祥失踪在问候名单中</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-08/china-s-former-defense-minister-wei-missing-from-greeting-list</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国前国防部长魏凤和没有出现在接受最高领导层问候的退休干部名单中，这是在军队官员遭到全面清洗之后出现的不寻常的遗漏。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-08/china-s-former-defense-minister-wei-missing-from-greeting-list</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 08 Feb 2024 03:43:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登再次迷惑欧洲领导人，交换科尔和默克尔</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-08/biden-again-confuses-european-leaders-swapping-kohl-and-merkel</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统乔·拜登再次混淆了欧洲国家元首，周三在纽约的筹款活动上向捐助者发表讲话时，两次将德国前总理赫尔穆特·科尔和德国前总理安格拉·默克尔混为一谈。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-08/biden-again-confuses-european-leaders-swapping-kohl-and-merkel</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 08 Feb 2024 03:38:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>巴基斯坦在选举日暂停移动电话服务</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-08/pakistan-stops-mobile-phone-services-nationwide-on-election-day</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周四，随着选民开始在大选中投票，巴基斯坦暂停了全国范围内的移动电话服务，称此举是为了在有争议的民意调查可能出现混乱之前维持秩序。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-08/pakistan-stops-mobile-phone-services-nationwide-on-election-day</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 08 Feb 2024 03:09:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>新加坡拒绝反对党审查储备政策的动议</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-08/singapore-rejects-opposition-motion-to-review-reserves-policy</link>
      <description><![CDATA[新加坡立法者周三拒绝了一项反对党动议，该动议建议政府应进一步动用国家储备，以帮助抵消不断上升的成本。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-08/singapore-rejects-opposition-motion-to-review-reserves-policy</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 08 Feb 2024 02:57:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>CBO 称移民将在十年内使美国 GDP 增长 7 万亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-08/immigration-to-boost-us-gdp-by-7-trillion-over-decade-cbo-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国国会预算办公室周三表示，移民激增将导致劳动力膨胀和需求增加，从而在未来十年为美国经济带来约 7 万亿美元的增长。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-08/immigration-to-boost-us-gdp-by-7-trillion-over-decade-cbo-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 08 Feb 2024 01:18:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>官方称海地警察在抗议期间打死 5 名武装环保人员</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-02-07/official-says-police-in-haiti-killed-4-armed-environmental-protection-agents-during-ongoing-protests</link>
      <description><![CDATA[海地太子港（美联社）——周三，在海地首都连续第三天的示威活动中，警方击毙了五名武装环保人员。示威活动导致该国陷入瘫痪，要求总理阿里尔·亨利辞职的呼声越来越高。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-02-07/official-says-police-in-haiti-killed-4-armed-environmental-protection-agents-during-ongoing-protests</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 07 Feb 2024 23:01:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>内塔尼亚胡犹豫不决，布林肯认为以色列与哈马斯达成协议的空间</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-07/blinken-says-hamas-response-on-hostages-creates-space-for-deal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[以色列和美国对哈马斯对暂停战斗并释放数十名人质提议的回应给出了相互矛盾的解释，总理本杰明·内塔尼亚胡似乎立即拒绝了这一提议，而国务卿安东尼·布林肯表示，这为达成协议打开了空间。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-07/blinken-says-hamas-response-on-hostages-creates-space-for-deal</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 07 Feb 2024 20:28:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>亚马逊、汇丰银行、AT&T 共同承诺在墨西哥雇用移民</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-07/un-partners-on-business-plan-to-hire-migrants-in-mexico</link>
      <description><![CDATA[亚马逊、汇丰控股和 AT&amp;T 等 50 家公司承诺在联合国移民机构的帮助下在墨西哥雇用移民，此举旨在为数千名移民中的一些人提供就业机会。近年来在这个拉丁美洲国家定居的外国人。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-07/un-partners-on-business-plan-to-hire-migrants-in-mexico</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 07 Feb 2024 12:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>里约热内卢在狂欢节前几天宣布登革热卫生紧急状态</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-02-05/rio-de-janeiro-has-declared-a-dengue-health-emergency-days-before-carnival-is-due-to-start</link>
      <description><![CDATA[里约热内卢（美联社）——里约热内卢周一宣布，由于爆发蚊媒登革热，该市宣布进入公共卫生紧急状态，就在巴西各地狂欢节庆祝活动开始前几天。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-02-05/rio-de-janeiro-has-declared-a-dengue-health-emergency-days-before-carnival-is-due-to-start</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 05 Feb 2024 18:24:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
